name: Parking in Helsinki
body:
### Helsinki Parking Ticket Machines

This project provides a REST API for parking ticket information. Ticket machine locations are originally provided by Helsinki Region Infoshare.

http://www.hri.fi/

http://www.hri.fi/en/data/helsingin-pysakointilippuautomaatit/
